data.description: BANK APPROVED PRICE. This three-story property is in the quiet and safe Gate of Lexington Plantation. The sizable kitchen and dining area are a chef's dream. With all stainless steel appliances, a double stove, granite countertops, custom backsplash, a large island/bar, and tons of cabinet space. The main level has beautiful hardwood floors and custom tile in the kitchen. Each of the six bedrooms provides plenty of space and storage. Enjoy entertaining on the back screened-in patio or in the large backyard. This house has great potential to become someone's next home.
